snippet.title: Funko Fusion - Sun Wukong Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Play as the legendary Monkey King in Funko Fusion! 

Get Sun Wukong as free DLC! Available now on Steam, PlayStation Store, and the Microsoft Store on Xbox.
